{"name": "explicit-python-django", "metadata": {"name": "explicit-python-django", "version": "1.0.2", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 5 - Production/Stable", "Environment :: Web Environment", "Framework :: Django :: 2.2", "Framework :: Django :: 3.0", "Framework :: Django :: 3.1", "Framework :: Django :: 3.2", "Framework :: Django :: 4.0", "Framework :: Django :: 4.1", "Framework :: Django :: 4.2", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "Natural Language :: Russian", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9"], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["explicit-python", "django"], "summary": "\u041d\u0430\u0431\u043e\u0440 \u043a\u043e\u043c\u043f\u043e\u043d\u0435\u043d\u0442\u043e\u0432 \u0434\u043b\u044f \u0438\u043d\u0442\u0435\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0438 explicit \u0441 django", "upload_time": 1732112040}, "documentation": ["# Explicit-Django\n## \u041d\u0430\u0431\u043e\u0440 \u043a\u043e\u043c\u043f\u043e\u043d\u0435\u043d\u0442\u043e\u0432 \u0434\u043b\u044f \u0438\u043d\u0442\u0435\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0438 Explicit \u0441 Django.\n\n### \u0411\u0430\u0437\u043e\u0432\u0430\u044f \u0435\u0434\u0438\u043d\u0438\u0446\u0430 \u0440\u0430\u0431\u043e\u0442\u044b \u043d\u0430 \u0442\u0440\u0430\u043d\u0437\u0430\u043a\u0446\u0438\u044f\u0445 Django ORM.\n\n```python\n# persons/core/unit_of_work.py\n\nfrom explicit.django.unit_of_work import BaseUnitOfWork\n\nfrom persons.core.persons.adapters.db import Repository as PersonsRepository\nfrom persons.core.persons.adapters.db import repository as persons_repository\n\n# (\u0438\u043c\u044f \u0430\u0442\u0440\u0438\u0431\u0443\u0442\u0430, \u0438\u043d\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d\u0441 \u0440\u0435\u043f\u043e)\nKNOWN_REPOS = (\n    ('persons', persons_repository),\n)\n\n\nclass UnitOfWork(BaseUnitOfWork):\n\n    persons: PersonsRepository\n\n    def __init__(self, *args, **kwargs):\n        super().__init__(*args, **kwargs)\n        self._registry.register(*KNOWN_REPOS)\n```\n\n### \u0414\u0435\u043a\u043e\u0440\u0430\u0442\u043e\u0440 \u0434\u043b\u044f \u043f\u0440\u0435\u043e\u0431\u0440\u0430\u0437\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u044f \u043e\u0448\u0438\u0431\u043e\u043a \u0432\u0430\u043b\u0438\u0434\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0438 \u043f\u0440\u0435\u0434\u043c\u0435\u0442\u043d\u043e\u0439 \u043e\u0431\u043b\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0438 \u0432 \u043e\u0448\u0438\u0431\u043a\u0438 \u0432\u0430\u043b\u0438\u0434\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0438 Django\n```python\nfrom explicit.django.domain.validation.exceptions import handle_domain_validation_error\n\nclass ViewSet(...):\n\n   @handle_domain_validation_error\n   def create(self, request, *args, **kwargs):\n       command = Command(...)\n       bus.handle(command)\n\n```\n## \u0417\u0430\u043f\u0443\u0441\u043a \u0442\u0435\u0441\u0442\u043e\u0432\n```sh\n$ tox\n```\n>>>>>>> e30984f (EDUEO-552 \u0412\u044b\u043d\u043e\u0441 \u0438\u043d\u0442\u0435\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0438 \u0441 django \u0432 \u043e\u0442\u0434\u0435\u043b\u044c\u043d\u044b\u0439 \u043f\u0430\u043a\u0435\u0442.)\n"], "modules": [{"name": "explicit.django.domain", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "explicit.django.domain.validation.exceptions", "documentation": ["\u0418\u0441\u043a\u043b\u044e\u0447\u0435\u043d\u0438\u044f \u043f\u0440\u0435\u0434\u043c\u0435\u0442\u043d\u043e\u0439 \u043e\u0431\u043b\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0438."], "functions": [{"name": "explicit.django.domain.validation.exceptions.handle_domain_validation_error", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "fn", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["\u041a\u043e\u043d\u0432\u0435\u0440\u0442\u0438\u0440\u0443\u0435\u0442 DomainValidationError \u0432 DjangoValidationError.\n\n```python\nclass ViewSet(...):\n    @handle_domain_validation_error\n    def create(self, request, *args, **kwargs):\n        command = Command(...)\n        bus.handle(command)\n```\n"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "explicit.django.domain.validation", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "explicit.django", "documentation": ["\u041d\u0430\u0431\u043e\u0440 \u043a\u043e\u043c\u043f\u043e\u043d\u0435\u043d\u0442\u043e\u0432 \u0434\u043b\u044f \u0438\u043d\u0442\u0435\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0438 Explicit \u0441 Django."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "explicit.django.unit_of_work", "documentation": ["\u0420\u0435\u0430\u043b\u0438\u0437\u0430\u0446\u0438\u044f \"\u0415\u0434\u0438\u043d\u0438\u0446\u044b \u0440\u0430\u0431\u043e\u0442\u044b\"."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "explicit.django.unit_of_work.BaseUnitOfWork", "bases": ["AbstractUnitOfWork"], "methods": [{"name": "explicit.django.unit_of_work.BaseUnitOfWork.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "savepoint", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "explicit.django.unit_of_work.BaseUnitOfWork._get_new_self", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "AbstractUnitOfWork", "xref": {"fqname": "explicit.unit_of_work.AbstractUnitOfWork", "project": "explicit-python"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "explicit.django.unit_of_work.BaseUnitOfWork.__enter__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "AbstractUnitOfWork", "xref"